---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Tooth Extractions" 
  category="Oral Surgery"
  description="Safe and comfortable tooth removal for severely infected or damaged teeth, followed by replacement options to restore your smile."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579684385127-1ef15d508118?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">When Removal is Necessary</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Sometimes a tooth is too severely infected or damaged to be saved. We perform safe, comfortable 
        extractions using local anesthetic, and always discuss replacement options to restore your smile 
        and oral function.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      When Tooth Extraction is Needed
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Common Reasons -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Common Reasons for Extraction</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-red-600 text-xs font-bold">!</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Severe Infection</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Infection has spread beyond what root canal therapy can treat</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-red-600 text-xs font-bold">!</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Extensive Decay</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tooth structure too damaged to support a filling or crown</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-red-600 text-xs font-bold">!</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Severe Fracture</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Crack or break extends below the gum line</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-red-600 text-xs font-bold">!</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Advanced Gum Disease</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tooth has lost too much supporting bone structure</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Other Situations -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Other Situations</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">i</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Orthodontic Treatment</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Creating space for proper tooth alignment</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">i</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Impacted Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Teeth that cannot properly emerge through the gums</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">i</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Overcrowding</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Too many teeth for the available space</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">i</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Preparation for Dentures</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Removing remaining damaged teeth before full denture placement</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Types of Extractions
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Simple Extraction -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Simple Extraction</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          For teeth that are visible in the mouth and can be removed easily. Most routine extractions 
          fall into this category.
        </p>
        
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Procedure:</h4>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
          <li>1. Local anesthetic is administered</li>
          <li>2. Tooth is loosened with dental instruments</li>
          <li>3. Tooth is gently removed with forceps</li>
          <li>4. Bleeding is controlled and healing instructions given</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <strong>Recovery:</strong> 1-3 days with minimal discomfort
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Surgical Extraction -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Surgical Extraction</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          For teeth that are broken at the gum line, impacted, or have complex root structures. 
          Requires more advanced techniques.
        </p>
        
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Procedure:</h4>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
          <li>1. Local anesthetic (possibly sedation)</li>
          <li>2. Small incision in the gum tissue</li>
          <li>3. Tooth may be sectioned for easier removal</li>
          <li>4. Extraction site is cleaned and sutured</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <strong>Recovery:</strong> 3-7 days with managed post-operative care
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What to Expect During Your Procedure
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Before</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            We'll review your medical history, take X-rays if needed, and explain the procedure. 
            Local anesthetic ensures you're comfortable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">During</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            You'll feel pressure but no pain. Simple extractions typically take just a few minutes. 
            We work efficiently while prioritizing your comfort.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">After</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            We'll provide detailed aftercare instructions and prescribe any necessary medications. 
            Follow-up appointments ensure proper healing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Post-Extraction Care
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 mb-4">What TO Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Bite on gauze for 30-45 minutes to control bleeding</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Apply ice packs for 15-20 minutes to reduce swelling</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Take prescribed medications as directed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Eat soft foods and drink plenty of fluids</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Rinse gently with salt water after 24 hours</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-700 mb-4">What NOT to Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Don't smoke or use tobacco products</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Avoid drinking through straws</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Don't spit forcefully or rinse vigorously</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Avoid hard, crunchy, or spicy foods</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Don't touch the extraction site with fingers or tongue</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Replacement Options After Extraction
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Dental Implants</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          Most natural-feeling permanent replacement option
        </p>
        <a href="/services/dental-implants" class="text-primary-900 font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Dental Bridge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          Fixed replacement that uses adjacent teeth for support
        </p>
        <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="text-primary-900 font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Partial Denture</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          Removable option for replacing one or several teeth
        </p>
        <a href="/services/dentures" class="text-primary-900 font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Comfortable & Safe Tooth Extraction
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        When extraction is necessary, we make the process as comfortable as possible. 
        We'll also help you explore the best replacement options to restore your smile.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/wisdom-teeth" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Wisdom Tooth Removal</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Specialized extraction service</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/dental-implants" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Implants</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Permanent tooth replacement</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/emergency-dental" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Emergency Dental Care</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Urgent tooth pain relief</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will the tooth extraction hurt?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        We use local anesthetic to ensure you're completely comfortable during the procedure. 
        You may feel pressure but should not experience pain. After the procedure, any discomfort 
        can usually be managed with over-the-counter pain relievers.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long does it take to heal after an extraction?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Initial healing typically takes 1-2 weeks, with the socket forming a blood clot within 24 hours. 
        Complete healing of the bone and gum tissue can take several months. Most patients return to 
        normal activities within a few days.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What is dry socket and how can I prevent it?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Dry socket occurs when the blood clot is dislodged from the extraction site, causing severe pain. 
        Prevent it by avoiding smoking, drinking through straws, spitting forcefully, and following all 
        post-operative instructions carefully.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Can I eat normally after tooth extraction?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Start with soft foods like yogurt, soup, and smoothies for the first few days. Gradually reintroduce 
        normal foods as comfort allows. Avoid hard, crunchy, or sticky foods near the extraction site 
        during the initial healing period.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>